This software implements the claude/channel capability of the Model Context
Protocol (https://modelcontextprotocol.io) and is designed to interoperate
with Claude Code (https://code.claude.com) by Anthropic.

The hdcd-telegram binary is a clean-room reimplementation of the Telegram
channel functionality. It is format-compatible with the official
telegram@claude-plugins-official plugin (Apache-2.0, Anthropic) but shares
no source code.
